page.title: 11 FAMILY LIFE IN WEEDON
page.content: *** MY FAMILY *** There are seven people in my family, my mum,dad,two brothers,two sisters,and myself. {My dad} has black hair and hazel brown eyes and works from 06.00 hours until 21.00 hours for a card firm and a car firm.{My mum} has brown hair and blue eyes,she delivers leaflets a lot of the time. My eldest brother is 14 years old and is very good at art.My older sister is 13 years old and is a good cook.My other brother is 10 years old and likes to draw animals.My youngest sister is 5 years old,she was born in a leap year and wants to be a nurse. I am 8 years old and have blonde hair and blue eyes.I like school a lot, especially when we do craft.
